
Note: 
   The necessary Raspberry binaries and the cross compiler/assembler are 
   downloaded from https://github.com/raspberrypi    

Download the RPI crosscompiler toolchain to directory tools-master:
 
 > make toolchain

Download binaries for RPI boot to directory sdcard:
  
 > make binaries

Then compile:
  
 > make

Install resulting kernel.img to sdcard directory:
 
 > make install

Then copy the contents of ./sdcard to a sdcard and boot RPI from it.




